message.body: The weather has me a little bit worried but it looks like we can squeak in a short walk at 6! Still work for you?
Yes. I may be a lil later - 6:10ish. My class goes til 5:30 - just depends how quickly I make it home.
Never mind. I'm not going to make it to my class so 6 should work.
OK. Either way. Which way did you want to walk? Let me know where I should meet you.
I'd like to go up #### and around the ###### if that works for u. There are some notices up about parking and I want to read these b4 committing to go to NJ tomorrow night.
Sounds fine. I'll meet you at your place then
Got ###############! Also got my picture taken by #####. Suppose I'll take the good with the weird today!
